Dan will be posting live updates from Rock and Shock on twitter @autumnseyes and reporting on the even for Metalunderground.com.</p><p>
<strong>Update:</strong> The Halloween costume contest winners have been announced (and can be seen) <a href="http://www.autumnseyes.com/entries.php">here</a>.</p></p>

		

